data.title: Saint John Maron Catholic Church
data.meta_description: Welcome to St. John Maron Maronite Catholic Church. Our site offers the opportunity to learn about our parish, stay updated with events, and become acquainted with the Maronite Church. We hope that you will also find inspiration here. Come and pray with us! CLERGY Pastor Rev. Antoine Bakh Subdeacons Subdeacon John Younes Subdeacon Charles Doche...
